xmpp_frontend release readme document
#####################################

This is NOT an OTP release. 

install
#######

from the xmpp_frontend directory

    make install

This will reconfigure, compile and install ejabberd and its 
dependency libexpat with the prefix xmpp_frontend/installation
prefixed with the absolute path to your current working directory.

Redo this step each time you move the location of xmpp_frontend
or erlang in your filesystem.

run
###

installation/sbin/ejabberdctl (start|stop|live)